message.distributionDefaultInviterIdTip.message: Default inviter's user ID, if the distribution link does not carry the inviter_id parameter, the default user ID will be used as the inviter.

message.distributionForceInviterIdTip.message: Force inviter's user ID, if this ID is set, it will be used as the inviter regardless of whether the distribution link carries the inviter_id parameter.

message.originTip.message: Site domain name, site configuration is bound to the domain name and cannot be changed.

message.titleTip.message: Site title, displayed in the browser tab.

message.descriptionTip.message: Site description, located in the site metadata, used for site SEO optimization.

message.logoTip.message: Site logo, displayed at the top of the site menu when the menu bar is expanded.

message.faviconTip.message: Site favicon, displayed in the browser tab.

message.adminsTip.message: Site administrator ID, the user who first creates the site will become the administrator, and only the site administrator can manage the site.

message.adminsTip2.message: You can add or delete administrator IDs here, and view user IDs at https://auth.acedata.cloud

message.keywordsTip.message: Site keywords, located in the site metadata, used for site SEO optimization.

message.keywordsTip2.message: You can add or delete website keywords here, the more precise the keywords, the more beneficial for SEO optimization.

message.featuresI18n.message: Open or close multi-language support, after closing, users can only use the default language.
